<topic id="display-problems-linux">
  <title>Display Problems on Linux or Solaris</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Display problem on Linux/Solaris</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>Display problems (such as screen freezes) on Linux or Solaris can be solved by <xref
        href="set-parameter-in-startup-script.dita">adding the startup parameter</xref>:
        <parmname>-Dsun.java2d.pmoffscreen=false</parmname>.</p>
  </body>
